{"type":"message","id":"a4e9c983","parentId":"29d20881","timestamp":"2026-03-28T08:19:12.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nGut, jetzt muss ich die eigentlichen SKILL.md Dateien lesen, um den Inhalt auf Sicherheitsrisiken zu prüfen. Besonders wichtig sind obsidian-cli (könnte Shell-Kommandos enthalten) und defuddle (nutzt ein externes Tool). Lass mich alle 5 SKILL.md Dateien parallel fetchen.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n\nJetzt die eigentlichen SKILL.md-Inhalte lesen — dort stecken die potenziellen Risiken:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_vb2c74pI7u6SZaWs3X5CIfAH","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"text","maxChars":10000,"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kepano/obsidian-skills/main/skills/obsidian-cli/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_k4xYez2YjMupJDJRnDmMVKKl","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"text","maxChars":5000,"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kepano/obsidian-skills/main/skills/defuddle/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_Ya5sb5HSwhiTcDtvTcHL7GuG","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"text","maxChars":10000,"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kepano/obsidian-skills/main/skills/obsidian-markdown/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_PY1Z4SQgX2ulrNzb6reDU7gT","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"text","maxChars":15000,"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kepano/obsidian-skills/main/skills/obsidian-bases/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_FZBFDFMGSAe01sflpopPY6sq","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"text","maxChars":10000,"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kepano/obsidian-skills/main/skills/json-canvas/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":130,"output":674,"cacheRead":18904,"cacheWrite":7695,"totalTokens":27403,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1